{"tid":248979,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【UGL醜聞】馮煒光又護主 斥立會查梁特屬政治炒作","createTime":"2017-05-19T03:40:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T03:41:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"424d436671ad4653cb667692f17187524519b479","tid":248979,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:40:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56713497&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170519\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56713497%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170519&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=eb473b50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56713497%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170519&h=9b5b8bef\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56713497&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170519</a><br />\n<br />\n【UGL醜聞】馮煒光又護主 斥立會查梁特屬政治炒作<br />\n<br />\n即時要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n2017-05-19 10:45:57 HKT<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n特首梁振英被揭發曾私下接觸民建聯周浩鼎，二人打龍通，修改立法會UGL專責委員會調查範圍的文件。民主派促周離開委員會，後來梁特卻反咬專業議政梁繼昌正被自己告誹謗，認為梁繼昌應避嫌不參與委員會工作。新聞統籌專員馮煒光今在報紙專欄加入戰團護主，批評立會調查UGL事件為政治炒作，稱只需20位議員同意，即可成立調查委員會，即可說特首被立法會調查，「這不是政治炒作又是什麼？」。<br />\n<br />\n文章題為「UGL事件的本和末」，馮煒光試圖為醜聞轉移視線，稱UGL事件近日被反對派炒得沸沸揚揚，但問題根本卻被刻意掩蓋。他重提梁特曾為自己辯護的理據，包括香港稅局未有向他追究任何款項、外國的執法機構未有跟進事件等。他又反問UGL於過去5年未有獲特區政府發出牌照、土地或經營權，「若有，即使政府不公布，UGL是澳洲上市公司，能不公布嗎？即使UGL不公布，其他人不會洩露嗎？」。"},{"pid":"dc67dc87e309bddc069be444ff982891d136b3db","tid":248979,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:41:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170519/large/1495161924_8326.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170519%2Flarge%2F1495161924_8326.jpg&h=4616fdff&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}